44:25.762 --> 44:27.998
Please, please, pretty please.

44:29.833 --> 44:31.965
- Ooh...
- [Anthony] Hello! Hello!

44:31.967 --> 44:34.802
Oh, thank you so much
for bringing all that.

44:34.804 --> 44:37.106
Yeah, no problem.
You look very nice.

44:37.806 --> 44:42.679
Oh! Thank you. It's, um... It's
just this little... Thank you.

44:43.146 --> 44:45.349
- Is there more outside?
- Yeah. Lots.

44:45.849 --> 44:47.815
- Did you get some sun?
- What?

44:47.817 --> 44:51.954
Um... uh, yeah, I, I, I,
I laid out with...

44:53.188 --> 44:57.293
with Cyd in the grass and I,
I got some... I got some sun.

44:57.793 --> 44:58.929
Hmm.

45:21.016 --> 45:24.353
- Some music?
- Uh, yes, yes, yes, yes.

