- Uh-huh.

46:00.190 --> 46:01.425
A friend friend?

46:02.826 --> 46:05.362
[Anthony chuckles]

47:02.619 --> 47:05.086
[Miranda] Oh, wonderful
and how long were you there?

47:05.088 --> 47:07.054
[female guest] I had a week...

47:07.056 --> 47:09.092
Relaxing.
Such a great time of the year...

47:09.659 --> 47:10.925
[Miranda]
You can go to Princeton.

47:10.927 --> 47:12.525
[male]
Absolutely, yes.

47:12.527 --> 47:13.994
I mean, I think that's wonderful.
We have these

47:13.996 --> 47:16.399
East Coast connections...

47:17.666 --> 47:19.435
- Hi.
- Hi.

47:19.969 --> 47:22.371
- Is this okay?
- It's perfect.

47:23.039 --> 47:24.307
It's amazing...

47:25.407 --> 47:27.108
- Welcome.
