47:28.610 --> 47:31.112
- Oh, and this is my niece. This is Cyd.
- Hi.

47:31.114 --> 47:33.246
Cyd, this is Ms. Evergreen,
Anthony's mom.

47:33.248 --> 47:34.347
Hi, pleased to meet you.

47:34.349 --> 47:35.485
- Welcome.
- Thank you.

47:36.751 --> 47:38.619
- My friend Thompson.
- How're you doing? Good to meet you.

47:38.621 --> 47:41.021
- He is also at the university with us.
- Okay.

47:41.023 --> 47:42.990
- I'm Jack.
- Jack, pardon me.

47:42.992 --> 47:45.025
- Hi.
- Of course, and this is his wife.

47:45.027 --> 47:46.529
- Hi, Cyd.
- Hi.

47:48.030 --> 47:52.032
And of course,
you remember Ridley from our...

47:52.034 --> 47:53.166
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

47:53.168 --> 47:55.371
- Nice tux.
- [laughs] Thanks.

48:00.710 --> 48:01.644
Okay.

