<i>♪ In the room next to mine ♪</i>

48:36.112 --> 48:39.048
Need a little bit of color. I don't want
people to think you're the caterer.

48:44.186 --> 48:45.288
I love it.

48:45.722 --> 48:48.456
<i>♪ I spoke it with fever ♪</i>

48:48.458 --> 48:49.590
Thank you.

48:49.592 --> 48:51.325
<i>♪ Put my foot down... ♪</i>

48:51.327 --> 48:54.461
- You like it?
- [elderly guest] I like it all. Charming.

48:54.463 --> 48:56.764
- Thank you!
- Have you ever been in Chicago before?

48:56.766 --> 48:58.068
No, it's my first time.

48:59.369 --> 49:01.538
Oh, then we'll have to go to that city.
It's a beautiful city.

49:02.704 --> 49:05.141
<i>♪ ...Drowning in shame ♪</i>

