58:59.300 --> 59:02.304
That...
That might've been a tie.

59:28.630 --> 59:30.896
- So glad you could come.
- Oh, thank you for having us.

59:30.898 --> 59:32.833
- Wonderful meeting you.
- And you as well, thank you.

59:32.835 --> 59:34.834
And congratulations, I hope
you can come back next month.

59:34.836 --> 59:36.639
- Absolutely. Bye.
- We'll see you there.

59:38.673 --> 59:41.878
- Where's Ridley?
- I think he and the girl are somewhere.

59:42.378 --> 59:44.744
- Oh, good God!
- Well, it happens.

59:44.746 --> 59:46.648
You know, I... I'll go get them.

01:00:08.871 --> 01:00:10.306
I'm sorry, um...

01:00:11.306 --> 01:00:14.143
- I...
- [Miranda knocking] Cyd?

01:00:14.376 --> 01:00:15.678
Yeah?

01:00:16.411 --> 01:00:19.915
- Is Ridley in there?
- Yeah.

01:00:20.181 --> 01:00:22.782
Ridley, your mothers
are looking for you.

01:00:22.784 --> 01:00:23.920
Okay.

